OL,6,FA dog owner whose Cane Corso cross
OL,7,Fmauled his younger brother to death in
OL,8,Fa "horrific" attack at their home has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FGary Stevens, 54, had previously
OL,12,Fadmitted to being the person in charge
OL,13,Fof a dog dangerously out of control
OL,14,Fcausing injury resulting in the death
OL,15,Fof his brother, 51-year-old Wayne
OL,16,FStevens.
OL,18,FThe attack happened in a house in
OL,19,FDerby at 5.50am on April 22 2023 and
OL,20,Fon Friday the court heard the dog was
OL,21,F"incredibly heavy".
