OL,6,FShe said: "He was threatening to turn
OL,7,Fthe dog on them and a number of
OL,8,Fofficers armed with Tasers pointed it
OL,9,Fat the dog and then fired them which
OL,10,Fincapacitated it as they tried to drag
OL,11,Fit towards the police van.
OL,13,F"But one Taser barbs came free and
OL,14,Farmed officers arrived and had no
OL,15,Fother option but to shoot the dog."
OL,17,FTony Stanford, mitigating, said his
OL,18,Fclient had taken the dog - called Ace
OL,19,F- from his niece who was unable to
OL,20,Flook after it as she had five children
OL,21,Fin her home.
